subject: Cross-Country Skiing
Speedskating
Olympic Games (2014)
Olympic Games (2014)
lead_paragraph: Abandoning their high-tech suits didn’t change the fortunes of the U.S. speedskaters, who failed to win a medal in the women’s 1,500 while the Netherlands won three.
